  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "School holidays from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to grant holidays to all schools nationwide from today to the 15th.",
        "This decision was taken in an online discussion between the education authorities.",
        "It has been decided to give a holiday to the students as transport problems continue due to the fuel crisis.",
        "Based on this, the Ministry of Education has also mentioned that the school education activities will start again on the 18th Monday. (a)"
      ],
